The '''Solenbaran Merchant Route''' was a remote [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperspace trade route]] that connected the distant world of [[Saclas]] with more profitable and populous worlds such as [[Etti IV/Legends|Etti IV]] and [[Bonadan/Legends|Bonadan]].<ref name="TEA" />

